<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Wallet - Hidden Moments</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 2rem auto; }
    nav a { margin-right: 1rem; }
    button { padding: 0.5rem 1rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Your Wallet</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="/wall">Wall</a>
    <a href="/create">Create Instant</a>
    <a href="/profile/<%= user.username %>">My Profile</a>
    <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
  </nav>
  <p>Current credits: <strong><%= user.credits %></strong></p>
  <h2>Get Free Credits</h2>
  <form action="/checkin" method="post">
    <button type="submit">Daily Check-in (+3 credits)</button>
  </form>
  <p>Come back once per day to earn free credits.</p>
  <h2>Buy Credits</h2>
  <p>The buy credits functionality is not implemented in this demo.</p>
  <p>In a real app, you could integrate Stripe or in-app purchases here.</p>
</body>
</html>